    <div class = "form">
    
    <h1>ADD A BRAND STATEMENT!</h1>
        <form action="`/profiles/${req.user.profile._id}`" method="POST">
            
  
  <div class="column">
    <label>Your Name</label>
    <input type="text" id="your_name" name="name"/>
    
    <label>Your Specialty</label>
    <input type="job" id="your_job" name="job" />
    
    <label>Brand Statement</label>
    <textarea id="brand" name="brandstatement" ></textarea>
    
</div>
   
  <div class="column" id = "brandstatement">
    
    <h2> What is a brand statement? </h2>

    <h3>Personal brand statements synthesize your personal brand in one to three sentences for your audience. When someone reads your personal brand statement they should understand who you are, professionally speaking, what you do, and the value that you offer. 
    </h3>
    <ul>
        <h4>Brand statements should answer the following questions:
        </h4>
        <li>What do you do?</li>
        <li>What problem do you solve?</li>
        <li>What are your passions and motivators?</li>
        <li>What value can you offer?</li><br>

        <p>&#169 2018 General Assembly </p>
    </ul>

  </div>
  
  <button class = "button" type = "submit">ADD MY BRAND</button>

</form>

